Otter Sauce

A Carolina-style mustard vinegar sauce that is great on pulled pork, any fatty meat, or greens like kale, collards, chard, etc.

1140 mL Koops stone ground mustard
990 mL apple cider vinegar
150 mL Molasses
60 mL brown sugar
60 mL Worstishire
120 mL mild hot sauce (Chululu)
500 mL water 
30 mL crushed red peppers

Combine, simmer briefly, bottle. Needs one week in bottle to blend flavors. 

Makes ~3 liters. 
